		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">47.104-4</ph> Contract clauses.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d2724e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2738e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            In order to ensure the application of <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                        scope="external"
                        format="html"
                        class="- topic/xref ">49 U.S.C. 10721</xref> and <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                        scope="external"
                        format="html"
                        class="- topic/xref ">1 3712</xref> rates, where authorized (see <xref href="FAR-i1071359.dita#i1071359"
                        base="i1071359"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">47.104</xref>(b)), insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1045527.dita#i1045527"
                        base="i1045527"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.247-1</xref>, Commercial Bill of Lading Notations, in solicitations and contracts when the contracts will be-</p>
					          <ol id="d2724e35" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2738e39" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Cost-reimbursement contracts, including those that may involve the movement of household goods (see <xref href="FAR-i1071395.dita#i1071395"
                              base="i1071395"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">47.104-3</xref>(b)); or</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2738e51" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Fixed-price f.o.b. origin contracts (other than contracts at or below the simplified acquisition threshold) (see <xref href="FAR-i1071384.dita#i1071384"
                              base="i1071384"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">47.104-2</xref>(b) and <xref href="FAR-i1071395.dita#i1071395"
                              base="i1071395"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">47.104-3</xref>).</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2738e68" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer may insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1045527.dita#i1045527"
                        base="i1045527"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.247-1</xref>, Commercial Bill of Lading Notations, in solicitations and contracts made at or below the simplified acquisition threshold when it is contemplated that the delivery terms will be f.o.b. origin.</p>
				        </li>
